   <h2> “黑帮老大”退隐江湖做电焊工 大规模造枪被擒 <a href="forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=432575&amp;page=1&amp;authorid=32991&amp;mobile=2" rel="nofollow" class="blue" style="font-size:12px;font-weight:normal;margin-left:10px;">只看楼主</a> </h2> 
   <div class="plc cl"> 
    <span class="avatar"><img src="http://www.b365t.com/memberserverb365thkkcm/avatar.php?uid=32991&amp;size=small" style="width:32px;height:32px;" /></span> 
    <div class="display pi" href="#replybtn_2053028"> 
     <ul class="authi"> 
      <li class="grey"> <em> 1<sup>#</sup></em><b> <a href="home.php?mod=space&amp;uid=32991&amp;mobile=2" class="blue">二传手</a></b> </li> 
      <li class="grey rela"> <em><a href="home.php?mod=spacecp&amp;ac=favorite&amp;type=thread&amp;id=432575&amp;mobile=2" class="favbtn blue">收藏</a></em> 2012-8-11 04:44:20</li> 
